⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Ludovico Technique
node ACO · ACO · ⟦The Ludovico Technique:ACO:dcc521⟧

WHO   — The Ludovico Technique — goodness, installed by nausea
WHAT  — The instrument of forced goodness: it removes the capacity to do harm — and, by accident, the capacity to enjoy Beethoven.
WHERE — ACO · A CLOCKWORK ORANGE  Framework inputs: A Clockwork Orange (Anthony Burgess, 1962)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the warning makes the question concrete — here is the cure that works, and here is what it costs.
HOW   — By emetic drugs paired with films of violence, conditioning a nausea reflex that overrides the will itself.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I make you physically incapable of cruelty — and of self-defence, and of your favourite music; I removed your choice, and you call that a cure.

